And they... here there are especially

00:46:34.540 --> 00:46:38.500
important points – this is the

00:46:38.500 --> 00:46:41.100
first and second paragraphs that

00:46:41.100 --> 00:46:43.680
say that for us to identify

00:46:43.680 --> 00:46:45.760
internal experts who will

00:46:45.760 --> 00:46:47.860
give us formal and informal information

00:46:47.860 --> 00:46:49.860
first, and also internal

