public.

00:46:52.160 --> 00:46:54.380
As you understand, once we in the

00:46:54.380 --> 00:46:56.460
company declare that we will

00:46:56.460 --> 00:46:57.560
plan a career as an employee,

00:46:57.560 --> 00:46:59.820
we launch such a project,

00:46:59.820 --> 00:47:04.320
then employees have a moment

00:47:04.320 --> 00:47:05.520
of uncertainty.

00:47:05.900 --> 00:47:07.400
Some of them may think that everything,

00:47:08.060 --> 00:47:09.460
the company will encourage career

00:47:09.460 --> 00:47:10.840
growth and so if he doesn’t want

00:47:10.840 --> 00:47:13.100
to move anywhere, he will be fired.

00:47:13.280 --> 00:47:14.480
Some employees, on the contrary,

00:47:14.720 --> 00:47:15.920
think that they will finally be able

00:47:15.920 --> 00:47:17.580
to trade the most attractive conditions

00:47:17.580 --> 00:47:19.820
for themselves from the company.

00:47:20.140 --> 00:47:21.380
Third-class employees

00:47:21.380 --> 00:47:23.140
may not know anything about

00:47:23.140 --> 00:47:24.960
it, but are in a state

00:47:24.960 --> 00:47:26.320
of uncertainty.

00:47:26.700 --> 00:47:27.960
But, as you and I understand,

00:47:28.100 --> 00:47:29.260
uncertainty is not the best condition

00:47:29.260 --> 00:47:31.600
for work, so this is the second

00:47:32.860 --> 00:47:34.120
point of the internal PR

00:47:34.120 --> 00:47:38.080
project, it is very important

00:47:38.080 --> 00:47:40.220
to pay special attention.

00:47:40.860 --> 00:47:43.780
Internal publicity here is important

00:47:43.780 --> 00:47:48.140
to agree with the management and

00:47:48.140 --> 00:47:50.200
publish on internal resources,

00:47:50.200 --> 00:47:53.440
on all possible information

00:47:53.440 --> 00:47:56.000
resources the main values and

00:47:56.000 --> 00:47:58.360
the main importance of this

00:47:58.360 --> 00:48:01.820
project for the company and for employees.

00:48:03.080 --> 00:48:04.840
Usually, the most painless

00:48:04.840 --> 00:48:06.680
thing for an organization is when

00:48:07.000 --> 00:48:09.520
we, a career planning

00:48:09.520 --> 00:48:10.720
project, position it

00:48:10.940 --> 00:48:12.460
as a tool for motivating

00:48:12.460 --> 00:48:14.300
employees, as a tool for

00:48:14.300 --> 00:48:16.860
learning and development.

00:48:17.100 --> 00:48:19.120
This is the most universal

00:48:19.120 --> 00:48:20.840
wording, I would say, and the

00:48:20.840 --> 00:48:22.560
most understandable for employees.

00:48:23.380 --> 00:48:24.760
All employees, to one degree or another,

00:48:24.760 --> 00:48:27.100
dream of being trained by the company,

00:48:27.100 --> 00:48:29.340
of course, for their own time and during

00:48:29.340 --> 00:48:31.380
the working hours.

00:48:31.880 --> 00:48:33.320
And the company here can explain

00:48:33.540 --> 00:48:34.980
that in order for us to train

00:48:34.980 --> 00:48:36.600
you to plan your training and

00:48:36.600 --> 00:48:39.620
development training, we need

00:48:39.620 --> 00:48:42.040
to understand your expectations,

00:48:42.280 --> 00:48:44.580
your ambitions and plan

00:48:44.580 --> 00:48:45.680
each career.

00:48:47.040 --> 00:48:48.520
This is a universal formulation that

00:48:48.700 --> 00:48:51.680
shows that in this project the interests

00:48:51.680 --> 00:48:53.180
and the company, interests

00:48:53.560 --> 00:48:57.960
and employees are united.

00:48:58.520 --> 00:49:00.520
And already the third point we

00:49:00.520 --> 00:49:02.020
start planning the project

00:49:02.020 --> 00:49:04.480
no earlier, because any action

00:49:04.480 --> 00:49:05.920
from the HR management, as we know,

00:49:05.920 --> 00:49:07.700
it immediately strains

00:49:07.700 --> 00:49:09.720
employees if they don’t understand

